/**
 * Universal Property Groups
 *
 * Only truly universal properties are defined here. Currently only "Color" is universal
 * because color is relevant across all store types and requires hex codes for proper display.
 *
 * All other properties (Size, Material, Volume, Scent, etc.) are store-specific and should
 * be generated by AI based on the store context. This ensures:
 * - Beauty stores get properties like "Volume", "Scent", "Skin Type"
 * - Fashion stores get properties like "Size", "Fabric", "Fit"
 * - Furniture stores get properties like "Material", "Dimensions", "Style"
 *
 * The color palette is comprehensive to cover most color names AI might generate.
 */

